column5: I know that this isn't the place but I just wanted say, Thank God for U.S. Navy SEALS! Happy Hole in the Head Day to everyone.
Inot in favor of killing but that being said.... AMEN
God Bless Our Special Operators:ONE and ALL!!
Note to self... don't mess with a Navy Seal. I guarantee he had a TON of security, and a small group of navy seals went in and did the job? Politics aside, I hope it brings peace and stability.
Couldn't have happened to a nicer, more deserving fellow. Good luck with that whole "virgin" thing.
Giving the order for the SEAL/CIA Teams to Go in was about the first good decision Obama has made! GOD BLESS OUR TROOPS!!!

Not a fan of Obama but I have to give him props today. He could have went the easy way out ( Clinton and his tomahawks) but he didn't. Sent in the bad asses so the SOB would be looking into American eyes when he took his last breath.
